# Shape

```
CONCEPT: QUANTUM_STATE

CENTROID
  A normalized vector in a complex Hilbert space.
  (It handles potentiality, not reality).

AXES
  Unitary Evolution (Smooth) ↔ Projective Measurement (Abrupt)
  Amplitude (Amount) ↔ Phase (Relationship)
  Entanglement (Shared Fate) ↔ Separability (Independence)
  Information ↔ Matter

SATELLITES
  The Bloch Sphere (Topology of a Qubit)
  Interference (Phases adding/subtracting)
  Born Rule (Probability = Amplitude²)
  Heisenberg Limit (Cannot know Fourier pairs simultaneously)

VOID
  ∅ Hidden Variables (Bell's Theorem says no local realism)
  ∅ "Particle" (Implies a tiny ball)
  ∅ "Wave" (Implies a medium)
  ∅ "Both at once" (Implies classical logical paradox)
  ∅ Observer = Consciousness (Observation is interactions)

TEXTURE
  The universe is detailed at the bottom.
  It is not fuzzy.
  It is just defined in a different coordinate system.
```

